(## 3\) Ranking method) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Facilities were ranked using:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- BP controlled % \(higher is better\)) Tj
T*
(- BP not controlled % \(lower is better\)) Tj
T*
(- Missed visits % \(lower is better\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Composite score:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`Score = 0.5 * \(BP controlled %\) + 0.3 * \(100 - BP not controlled %\) + 0.2 * \(100 - Missed visits) Tj
T*
(%\)`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(To reduce distortion from very small sites, a minimum volume filter was applied:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- **Included in main ranking:** facilities with >= 500 registered HTN patients) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(District benchmark \(same report\):) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- BP controlled: 54%) Tj
T*
(- BP not controlled: 26%) Tj
T*
(- Missed visits: 17%) Tj
